      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified against alternative formulations; sensitivity of QOIs to model-form choices quantified.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model selected without comparison to Giersiepen-Wurzinger or modified Bludszuweit formulations. Model-form uncertainty is unquantified."
    },
