      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional analysis confirms dynamic similarity between validation experiment and intended COU; any deviations corrected or bounded.",
      "rationale": "Dimensional similarity between bench-top validation experiment and clinical VAD operating conditions has not been formally evaluated. Reynolds number and exposure-time scaling are unverified."
